Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.47,0:00:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.43,0:00:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worried that this full tank of energy will lose it's destination
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoever shakes for just a minute their boredom, will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.84,0:00:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ride, atop the white line, Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sit down, in the place you have faith Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go to the place that tempts you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.32,0:00:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If each person took one thing at a time, freedom and passion in their hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.58,0:00:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the shine to come, continue our journey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.72,0:00:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unclear everyday trump-card that sustains me, is your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.91,0:01:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The best growth is coming forth, unstoppable wild drive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.97,0:01:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are both yet to settle down, striking the door
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Big Five pulled out there trump card, the Five God Dragon, to fight us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.72,0:01:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But the combined power of me and Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1} had enough Attack Points to bring it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.44,0:01:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We beat the Big Five and won the Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.15,0:01:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Honda-{\i0}kun{\i1}'s body didn't return.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.40,0:01:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the Big Five were wiped out by Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Noah! What in the world are you planning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Noah VS Seto:\N Duel of the Creation of Heaven and Earth"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.92,0:01:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you think you're doing, OOH-AH~!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:02:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda, I'm sorry. I don't think you're gonna be returning to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell you are, OOH!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.43,0:02:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't just ignore Mokuba when he was captured by Noah, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And just how the hell is that related to you turning me upside down, OOH-AHH~!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.85,0:02:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're at a dead end right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only clue we've got to find them and figure out how to get out of this world is the body you're in that was made here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have some sort of secret switch, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CUT IT OUT, OOH-AH!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a ton of em.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.79,0:02:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck was that? Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this button?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one looks like an\N emergency button to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Emergency Mode! Emergency Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Kaiba Land!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're here to welcome me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Welcome, Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I invite you to my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother, who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks a lot like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A guest will be coming here shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go make some preparations before his arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You be a good boy and wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba and his brother are here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where did Honda-{\i1}san{\i0} go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait up Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only staff and personal are permitted beyond this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.47,0:04:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only staff and personal are permitted beyond this point!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:04:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means there's something behind here we shouldn't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you do not leave willingly you will be made to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, Honda-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's up, ooh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, Seto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard! Where's Mokuba?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fret over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fret over it. Regardless of how our destiny pulls us into fray, this doesn't involve Mokuba. He will be released.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside Seto, isn't this place beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We stand atop the Earth\N before it was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can create any world you want using Kaiba Corporation's advanced simulator,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whether it be the universe\N or a pit of magma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using this, even be it a war contrived by a revolution on the verge of society,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's possible to thrust\N mankind into a new age.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's something you want to say to me, how about you just come out and say it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am appalled by you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only use this outstanding technology on worthless games!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, isn't it about time we settle things?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And for us to decide who is most suitable to run Kaiba Corporation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because, Noah, you're already {\i1}dead{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it on that video!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:06:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this supposed to be\N Noah's funeral service?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's true, this means Noah's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, but that's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then who's the Noah who's been talking to us this whole time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw those old records?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that will make\N this go much faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. It's true that my body is made up of virtual flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm much different up {\i1}here{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold, Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the container\N holding my true brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My conscious lies dormant inside it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Come over here, ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a railroad over here, ooh-ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:08:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} went this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way to tell that, ooh-ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no other paths we can take.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've just got to check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But should we just wait and hope a train comes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found something useful, OOH~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, monkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared~!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going way too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, whatcha talkin' about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hold on tighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoo yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you say that, we're seriously going too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi! Hit the breaks! The breaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean... these...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... your brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:09:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Just like you said, my body is certainly dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But everything {\i1}started{\i0} the moment of my death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Born the only son of Kaiba Corporation,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was spoiled more than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if I was born superior\N to all other children.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I had already been selected to take over Kaiba Corporation someday, my lifestyle had been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father invested in the most elite teachers to ensure I received a top-level education.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In not just studying...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But also music...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...sports...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he wanted me to grow up to be a person at the top of all fields, someone on par with a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I tried my best to answer my father by doing the best I could all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Had things gone on that way, you and Mokuba would have never been adopted by Kaiba Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said before that life is a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:10:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, you almost say I was cheated...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Noah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.50,0:10:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}NOAH!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Make Noah like he was before!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}B-But, sir...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you disobeying me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why the hell were you hired?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm terribly sorry, but in his current condition...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're nothing but a pathetic quack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're useless to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say the human brain is made up of electronic-like signals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father had all of my memories transferred
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,into an AI Computer,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a system invented by Kaiba Corporation for war.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was granted a new life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And afterwards, Seto, you and Mokuba were taken in by the Kaiba's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father took you in as a my rival and my motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were intended to push me further in my studies, all the way to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, you were never intended to inherit Kaiba Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I trust you won't have any complaints...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if we use the thing you're most comfortable with, Duel Monsters, to decide my victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:12:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm positive you'll be most satisfied losing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll inherit your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be used for the benefit of Kaiba Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're basically saying all of my suffering, all of my aggravation and my entire life occurred for {\i1}you{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That about sums it up. And if you do what I want now, it'll save you a humiliating loss later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen well, Noah! I've never lived for anyone but myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My future is decided\N on a road of glory!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you insist on blocking that road, whoever it may be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll eliminate you with\N my own two hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, you don't know when to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You run your mouth too much, Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My deck has already been decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for my Deck Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Kaiser Seahorse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been dreaming of this moment for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's have our match, Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DUEL!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go, Noah!\N My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.86,0:13:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Giant Virus in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then set a card face-down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Noah, the Goddess of Victory smiles over me in this Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The card I have set is the Deck Destruction Virus of Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Its effect activates the very moment you attack the Giant Virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every Monster in your hand or deck holding 1500 or greater Attack Points will be wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.60,0:13:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn comes to an end here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:13:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going now, Seto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:14:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Chiron the Mage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That {\i1}hurt{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-{\i1}What{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this space?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! Look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends are all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got here just in time to watch my Duel with Seto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I get to show you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Creation of Heaven and Earth Deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Creation of Heaven and Earth Deck"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Special Ability of Chiron the Mage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror of Truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiron the Mage's Mirror of Truth allows me to see the face-down card on my opponent's field and destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, that set card you've got is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Deck Destruction Virus of Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw through your entire plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Chiron!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack the Giant Virus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Giant Virus's Special Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Regenerative Ability, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.75,0:15:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you got rid of my Death Virus, my victory hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sacrifice Giant Virus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Vampire Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vampire Lord, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disciple of Darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now for Vampire Lord's\N Vampiral Effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each time I damage you, I must declare one type of card in which you must send to the Graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah, toss away a Monster Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not too shabby, Seto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But such an evil Monster does not fit in well with the holy land I've created.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demons shall be sent back to the darkness they came from!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card! Fissure!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then Summon Celestial Warrior Aries!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good! Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} just\N lost his Wall Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Aries!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct Attack!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s Life...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the same Kaiba we know getting beaten so easily...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then place one set card.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That ends my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what's wrong, Seto?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this all the strength your prestiged Power Deck can muster?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't take me seriously, this match will be over before you even realize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or, perhaps, you've been taking me seriously {\i1}all along{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Noah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revive, Vampire Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vampire Lord holds two Abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first is a Vampiral Ability designed to assault your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when he is destroyed by one of your Card Effects,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his Immortality Ability lets me revive him on the turn after you do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will also Summon Newt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet! Now Kaiba's got two Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for a counterattack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:18:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some never dirtying my holy land with evil Demon-Types.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah, if you want to keep on pretending you're the creator of this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then allow me to {\i1}descend{\i0} to that world alongside you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack, Vampire Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're long-winded, Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will return those evil souls to where they came from!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Card, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Reformation!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Reformation makes me pick two Attributes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You then must choose one of the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Following, all Monsters on the field holding that Attribute are destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have chosen the Wind Attribute and the Darkness Attribute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So choose whichever you like, Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Vampire Lord is a Dark Attribute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Newt is a Wind Attribute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Vampire Lord has more Attack Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.69,0:18:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:19:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I choose Vampire Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.95,0:19:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now be gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vampire Lord!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you do that, Kaiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just picked the Monster with higher Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's got his reasons!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vampire Lord will be recovered next turn thanks to his Card Effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! Kaiba can just recover him next turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that I still\N have Newt on my field.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Newt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.69,0:19:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Graviton Punch!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just about equal now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah and Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} both use Power Decks - calling out extremely powerful Monsters instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If either of them holds back even a little in this Duel, they'll lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:20:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Long ago, when evil beings roamed the earth, God washed them all away."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that time is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.59,0:20:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giant Flood!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta get outta here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nowhere to run!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Newt's being taken away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! All the Monsters in the Graveyard, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:21:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It {\i1}means{\i0} that my Deck Master Ability has just been activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Deck Master?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, my Deck Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.33,0:21:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ark of Miracles!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...his Deck Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.39,0:21:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, this is where the Duel of the Creation of Heaven and Earth {\i1}really{\i0} begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A huge ark appears behind Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Noah's Deck Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.94,0:21:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of power does this Deck Master have?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.87,0:21:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what does he mean when he says, "This is where the seven turns of creation starts"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.83,0:21:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On a field that changes scenery each and every turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.41,0:21:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sparks fly as Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}\N and Noah clash fiercely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:22:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take my eyes off their fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.96,0:22:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Invincible Deck Master - Ark of Miracles"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.51,0:22:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.99,0:22:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, wherever it rises
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.90,0:22:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A dream is a dream, and it won't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.17,0:22:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The straight rail and the steep route
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.85,0:22:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To go, or not go all of yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.24,0:22:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm getting tired of counting my advances in a cage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.80,0:22:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Respect! Boys, show me your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.39,0:22:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's awkward, but draw the map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now let's walk forever with our head up high...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.31,0:23:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, if it starts to get to familiar like you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.12,0:23:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}answer freely to the everyday discomfort
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.90,0:23:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to believe you, because I am losing my way with everything
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.88,0:23:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hiding in my heart... this secret paradise
